{"tid":2338927,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【聖誕快樂】徐承恩：香港人必須背起國族自決的十字架。這是上帝的召命。","createTime":"2020-12-24T09:56:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T11:48:42.000Z","uid":138409,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"634b27344c127e0450406d4d6b7cfda4c1c9cb47","tid":2338927,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:56:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10159414333155530&amp;id=564615529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10159414333155530%26id%3D564615529&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MVIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=dcfa9ee5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10159414333155530&amp;id=564615529</a><br />\n<br />\n耶穌寶誕，普天同慶，歡樂異常。可是，「這孩子將來是要死的」。這是祂降生的使命：背起十字架，在髑髏地受死，以自我犧牲戰勝黑暗。<br />\n<br />\n在主曆2019年，反送中運動在頌讚上主的歌聲中得以紥根。哈利路亞。耶穌親身顯靈，擋住服事強權的黑警，直接向中國這個事奉撒旦的邪惡帝國下戰書。可是這位神明，卻從未保證天色常藍、花香常溢。衪只是以身作則，呼召我們背起十字架，唯有學懂背負自己的命運，方有可能承受天命、得蒙救贖。<br />\n<br />\n如今魔道橫行，苦難日增。但香港人必須背起國族自決的十字架。這是上帝的召命。"},{"pid":"36014c18f0038b881f78a65918c2a7647406b17d","tid":2338927,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:58:37.000Z","msg":"耶膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede181224af46a83343a1153f67c0bec8386a001","tid":2338927,"uid":23874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9698bcea55b99a5da57075c2c12d34c7ce8728","tid":2338927,"uid":156913,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:06:11.000Z","msg":"who are you?<br />\n777夠話聽到天父聲音啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf59c3c312c2f5a7faf38ed8630b3dbfcf7dbad","tid"